title: 115: Did We Actually Write Our Book? | Ear Biscuits Ep. 115
description:
On the eve of their book release, Rhett & Link sit down to discuss their creative process, share some stories found between its covers, and earnestly address the question of "Did we write our book?" in this week's Ear Biscuits.

Listen to Ear Biscuits at: 

Apple Podcasts: http://apple.co/29PTWTM

Spotify: http://spoti.fi/2oIaAwp
